    Black Aracnia put the bowcaster in its holster and noisely dragged the 
unconscience Quickstrike to the brig. She locked his cell and left him with a 
pack of ration that would sustain him.
    Returning to the bridge she saw the rodent still pokeing around outside. 
Enough was enough.
    "Listen, Darkmouse, I have your Quickstrike prisoner. I suggest you go 
now or I will definetly hurt him. Shew, go now, before I sic the Autoguns on 
you!"
